    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been really well-taken care of over the years. It has a few minor signs of use here and there, but it runs like a dream and is looking for a great new home. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
