    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example remains mechanically robust with a recently overhauled Double VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, while the suspension retains its communicative feedback. Showing honest wear consistent with its age, this M3 remains a visceral, high-revving driver\u2019s tool ready for the canyon or the track.",
